爭是我們成立的使命<br />\n#已經開始研究進化版和你唱<br />\n#我們絕不會以眾籌方式籌集營運資金<br />\n#敬請密切留意我們各Channel<br />\n<br />\n《創新文宣方式起源》<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=120101039608164&amp;id=106770030941265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D120101039608164%26id%3D106770030941265&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=7b35b21a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=120101039608164&amp;id=106770030941265</a><br />\n<br />\n《開發研究及生產過程》<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=125684132383188&amp;id=106770030941265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D125684132383188%26id%3D106770030941265&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=85ee7ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=125684132383188&amp;id=106770030941265</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n*請關注我們頻道:<br />\n*Please follow our channel:<br />\nFacebook: <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3a31vWb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3a31vWb&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=638907e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3a31vWb</a><br />\nTelegram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VmUMRH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VmUMRH&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=b0065482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VmUMRH</a><br />\nInstagram :<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3a3pdBC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3a3pdBC&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=4b4a3227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3a3pdBC</a><br />\nYouTube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Vke6iq\" data-sr-url=\"https